he freedom group in september  as the north carolinabased gun maker searched for a permanent ceo in march  he stepped down as ceo of the freedom group and as the head of the operations and advisory business of cerberus capital management lp referencesedit  portfolios worst american ceos of all time cnbccom  retrieved    robert l nardelli nndbcom retrieved    flaherty joseph  december  how home depot copied apple to build an ingenious new bucket wiredcom condé nast retrieved  september  in  marcus retired and brought on bob nardelli as ceo nardelli had been one of jack welchs hatchet men at ge and he spent the next seven years driving down costs—at the expense of home depots reputation for innovationmarcus forced nardelli out in  and brought in a home depot veteran to right the ship by returning the focus to developing and selling innovative products exclusive to home depot   nardellis downfall its all about the stock archived january   at the wayback machine  lublin joann s zimmerman ann terhune chad january   behind nardellis abrupt exit the wall street journal   joe nocera the board wore chicken suits new york times  may   vlasic bill robert nardelli  the new york times topicsnytimescom retrieved    nardellibush article that mentions presidential council archived may   at the wayback machine  paul harris article that mentions bush nardelli garden reception observerguardiancouk retrieved    financial times story about nardellis salary  httpswebarchiveorgwebhttpsportsyahoocomnascarnewsslugapnascardaytonaprovaptypelgns archived from the original on february   retrieved september    missing or empty title help   cnn nardelli inverview transcriptscnncom retrieved    greg gardner free press business writer  nardelli says chrysler financial needs second round of loans detroit free press freepcom retrieved    pay rule led chrysler to spurn loan washington post washingtonpostcom retrieved    marchionne confirmed as postch chrysler ceo autoblogcom retrieved    next chrysler